title: >>> Pick YOUR Poster !
body_text:
DODGEBALL 26 is making history before it even happens.
For the second time ever, a collosal vote will decide which poster you, the people, like the best. The poster with the most votes becomes the official DODGEBALL 26 logo; it's that simple.
Those that remember the first contest will recall Justin Pierce winning. There are some new challengers this time around, but only one will have the privelege of having their poster become the official logo.
_____________
**Please do not leave a comment with your answer. Rather send them to Undertaker15yrs or WWECoowner screennames. Answers can also be emailed to Undertaker13yrs@aol.com**
_____________
#1>>
*Various Players*
#2>>
*Lauren Winston/Backlash Mixture*
#3>>
*Cupid/Valentine Logo*
#4>>
*Various Players*
#5>>
*"Change" Logo*
#6>>
*College Sylabus*
